Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
his industrial tract is strategically located on Beaver Street three quarters of a mile west of Chaffee Road and one mile east of the new Beltway, HWY 23. It has 3,300 feet of I-10 frontage. Access to the property is via Cylinder Lane.

Located just minutes from Cecil Commerce Center, this is an ideal location for distribution or logistical support in a fast-growing region of Jacksonville-Northeast Florida.
